13/*
14 * The routines really come from the Levitte Programming, so to make life
15 * simple, let's just use the raw files and hack the symbols to fit our
16 * namespace.
17 */
18#define LP_DIR_CTX OPENSSL_DIR_CTX
19#define LP_dir_context_st OPENSSL_dir_context_st
20#define LP_find_file OPENSSL_DIR_read
21#define LP_find_file_end OPENSSL_DIR_end
22
23#include "internal/o_dir.h"
24
25#define LPDIR_H
26#if defined OPENSSL_SYS_UNIX || defined DJGPP \
27 || (defined __VMS_VER && __VMS_VER >= 70000000)
28# include "LPdir_unix.c"
29#elif defined OPENSSL_SYS_VMS
30# include "LPdir_vms.c"
31#elif defined OPENSSL_SYS_WIN32
32# include "LPdir_win32.c"
33#elif defined OPENSSL_SYS_WINCE
34# include "LPdir_wince.c"
35#else
36# include "LPdir_nyi.c"
37#endif
